Installation Guide

Get started with Quantum Code in under 10 minutes. Complete setup guide with step-by-step instructions.

Step-by-Step Setup

pip install quantum-code

Install Quantum Code via pip package manager

Latest stable version from PyPI

quantum-code --version

Verify installation and check version

Confirm successful installation

quantum-code configure

Set up your AI model API keys securely

Configure OpenAI, Anthropic, and Google API keys

quantum-code setup

Configure analysis preferences and defaults

Set up model preferences and output formats

quantum-code analyze src/

Run your first code analysis

Analyze your codebase with multiple AI models

Quick Start Checklist

  • Choose your AI models (at least one required)
  • Get API keys from respective providers
  • Install Quantum Code via pip
  • Run configuration wizard
  • Start analyzing your code
